<a href="https://github.com/webpack-contrib/less-loader/actions" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://github.com/webpack-contrib/less-loader/workflows/less-loader/badge.svg" alt="tests" /></a>
<a href="https://codecov.io/gh/webpack-contrib/less-loader" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://codecov.io/gh/webpack-contrib/less-loader/branch/master/graph/badge.svg" alt="cover" /></a>
